{"pr_number": 1019, "pr_title": "[plugin-mobile-app] Add step to clear field", "pr_createdAt": "2020-10-13T11:28:52Z", "pr_url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019", "timeline": [{"oid": "8994d431d8fde395eb530f9a690555348a11bc7a", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/commit/8994d431d8fde395eb530f9a690555348a11bc7a", "message": "[plugin-mobile-app] Add step to clear field", "committedDate": "2020-10-13T11:54:14Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "2c8ee0050ea0d3a030bc7e4da10bbf20e2b79082", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/commit/2c8ee0050ea0d3a030bc7e4da10bbf20e2b79082", "message": "[plugin-mobile-app] Add step to clear field", "committedDate": "2020-10-13T12:24:52Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzkxODMwMQ==", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019#discussion_r503918301", "bodyText": "why is this check needed?", "author": "valfirst", "createdAt": "2020-10-13T12:42:31Z", "path": "vividus-plugin-mobile-app/src/main/java/org/vividus/mobileapp/action/KeyboardActions.java", "diffHunk": "@@ -75,4 +76,23 @@ public void typeText(WebElement element, String text)\n             webDriverProvider.getUnwrapped(HidesKeyboard.class).hideKeyboard();\n         }\n     }\n+\n+    /**\n+     * Clear the <b>element</b>'s text\n+     * <br>\n+     * The atomic actions performed are:\n+     * <ol>\n+     * <li>check if the element's text is empty</li>\n+     * <li>if the element's text is not empty then clear the element, otherwise do nothing</li>\n+     * </ol>\n+     * @param element element to clear, must not be {@code null}\n+     */\n+    public void clearText(WebElement element)\n+    {\n+        String elementText = element.getText();\n+        if (!StringUtils.isEmpty(elementText))", "originalCommit": "2c8ee0050ea0d3a030bc7e4da10bbf20e2b79082", "replyToReviewId": null, "replies": [{"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzk3MDkzMA==", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019#discussion_r503970930", "bodyText": "getText is ~5 times faster than clear command, so if field is empty we will not spend time on clearing it", "author": "uarlouski", "createdAt": "2020-10-13T13:53:42Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzkxODMwMQ=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzk3OTI5NA==", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019#discussion_r503979294", "bodyText": "any platform?\n5x, but what is absolute value? is it like 1ms vs 5ms or 1 min vs 5 min?", "author": "valfirst", "createdAt": "2020-10-13T14:03:56Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzkxODMwMQ=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwNDE4Mjc4MA==", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019#discussion_r504182780", "bodyText": "iOS platform: ~300ms vs ~1600ms", "author": "uarlouski", "createdAt": "2020-10-13T18:50:29Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzkxODMwMQ=="}, {"id": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwNDQ3Njg4OQ==", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/pull/1019#discussion_r504476889", "bodyText": "So in the most common case it is 1600 + 300 = 1800 ? :)", "author": "ikalinin1", "createdAt": "2020-10-14T07:58:49Z", "replyToReviewId": "MDI0OlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3Q29tbWVudDUwMzkxODMwMQ=="}], "type": "inlineReview"}, {"oid": "6c6b867418f1a8b51ab4c21698272b08800a5f11", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/commit/6c6b867418f1a8b51ab4c21698272b08800a5f11", "message": "[plugin-mobile-app] Add step to clear field", "committedDate": "2020-10-13T13:55:07Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "ccb329378a45ff5b87986d44a6732ee8847bd0d3", "url": "https://github.com/vividus-framework/vividus/commit/ccb329378a45ff5b87986d44a6732ee8847bd0d3", "message": "[plugin-mobile-app] Add step to clear field", "committedDate": "2020-10-13T16:06:48Z", "type": "forcePushed"}, {"oid": "ead